=======

A dramatization of the methods in which young women are abducted or
otherwise procured for prostitution.

Annie, a "good girl with a strong work ethic" falls prey to a
"procurer" who seduces her and tricks her into a sham marriage.
Completely dependent, Annie has no choice but to do what her pimp say.

Shot on location in red-light districts in Denver and El Paso.
Constucted from the two (of four) surviving 35mm reels in the
Library of Congress.

Intertitles are used to explain missing scenes.
